'''芝加哥大学'''（{{lang-en|University of Chicago}}），简称'''芝大'''（{{Lang|en|UChicago}}），位于[[美国|美国]][[伊利诺伊州|伊利诺伊州]][[芝加哥|芝加哥]]的[[私立|世界顶级私立]][[研究型大学|研究型大学]]，[[美洲大学协会|美洲大学协会]]12个创始会员之一，常年位列各大学排行榜世界前十。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.shanghairanking.com/ARWU2016.html|title=ARWU World University Rankings 2016 {{!}} Academic Ranking of World Universities 2016 {{!}} Top 500 universities {{!}} Shanghai Ranking - 2016|accessdate=2017-01-16|work=www.shanghairanking.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313212444/http://www.shanghairanking.com/ARWU2016.html|archive-date=2017-03-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/world-university-rankings/2016|title=QS World University Rankings 2016|date=2016-08-25|newspaper=Top Universities|accessdate=2017-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171130013658/https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/world-university-rankings/2016|archive-date=2017-11-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.timeshighereducation.com/world-university-rankings/2017/world-ranking#!/page/0/length/25/sort_by/rank/sort_order/asc/cols/stats|title=World University Rankings|date=2016-08-17|newspaper=Times Higher Education (THE)|accessdate=2017-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161231113411/https://www.timeshighereducation.com/world-university-rankings/2017/world-ranking#!/page/0/length/25/sort_by/rank/sort_order/asc/cols/stats|archive-date=2016-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.usnews.com/education/best-global-universities/rankings?int=a27a09|title=Best Global Universities Rankings (US NEWS)|accessdate=|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202234456/http://www.usnews.com/education/best-global-universities/rankings?int=a27a09|archive-date=2017-02-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>

芝加哥大学1890年由石油大王[[约翰·戴维森·洛克菲勒|约翰·洛克菲勒]]创办，包括大學学院以及由4个学术部门、6所职业学院和1所[[继续教育|继续教育]]学院组成的各种研究生项目和跨学科委员会，并拥有约6000名學士生和10,000名研究生。<ref>{{Cite web|title=History|url=http://www.uchicago.edu/about/history/|accessdate=2017-01-16|work=The University of Chicago|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161126001825/http://www.uchicago.edu/about/history/|archive-date=2016-11-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Academics|url=http://www.uchicago.edu/academics/|accessdate=2017-01-16|work=The University of Chicago|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170117005436/http://www.uchicago.edu/academics/|archive-date=2017-01-17|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在世界范围内，芝加哥大学在[[伦敦|伦敦]]、[[北京|北京]]、[[香港|香港]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]、[[德里|德里]]等地设有中心机构或校区。<ref>{{Cite web|title=University of Chicago Global|url=https://global.uchicago.edu/|accessdate=2019-08-04|work=global.uchicago.edu|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331050304/https://global.uchicago.edu/|archive-date=2019-03-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>

